On Jun 22, 2004, at 7:30 AM, Anson Lau wrote:

> Hi guys,
>
> Lets say I want to search the term "hello world" over 3 fields with
> different boost:
>
> ((hello:field1 world:field1)^0.001 (hello:field2 world:field2)^100
